Who We Are


 Who We Are Our Core Business Our History Corporate Governance Security and Privacy Frequently Asked Questions 











Scotiabankers are dedicated to helping our 23 million customers become better off through a broad range of advice, products and services, including personal and commercial banking, wealth management and private banking, corporate and investment banking, and capital markets. 
Founded in 1832 in Halifax, Nova Scotia, our growth has always been fuelled by the success of our customers and our longevity secured by an unshakable commitment to carefully and expertly managing risk and capital.
That focus on doing what’s right for customers – short and long term – has made us a leading financial services provider in North America, Latin America, the Caribbean and Central America, and Asia-Pacific.
Headquartered in Canada, we are a team of approximately 89,000 Scotiabankers. Each of us are committed to being the best at understanding our customers’ needs and all of us working together to deliver practical advice and relevant solutions that help our customers become better off.

